You are sleeping in this reality and cannot awoke. U cannot hear the winds. [Your Arete does not exist or it is too faint to be seen].
You seem to be able to bend the wind. But without a teacher, nothing comes of it. [Your Arete is just beginning to take shape, you don’t realize how much you are changing, at least not yet].
You are more capable than most and your strengths have been recognized by someone significant. [Your Arete strives to ascend, but first you must choose what kind of magician you will become].

You have become an adept of the chosen path. Now you need to learn and cognize in order to develop yourself and find those who will go with you together.  [Your Arete removes the limitations of knowledge from you, mysticism and empiricism fill your world with colors.].

You have developed yourself and become a young magician, now you can overcome any obstacle, read any book. Master more things to nourish yourself with the juice of the colors of magic. [Your Arete is burning, thirsting for something new, it is like a flaring fire of bright orange flashes.].

You assert your power in this world by collecting a collection of powerful artifacts. Your teachers appreciate you, you are worth considering. [A purple shade appears in your Arete, the Dream has now become more pliable for you. ].

You have become more attentive to mysticism and incredible coincidences of fate. Stasis echoes your requests and opens up new paths for you....  [Your Arete allows you to go deeper into the blue of yourself. ].

You have completed the basics of your training, now you can become an archmage and stop on your path. But do you really want this? [Your Arete has reached new horizons, now transformations of your body are given to you with incredible simplicity and your essence gives off emerald azure.]

You are so skilled in the winds of magic that your fingertips now create colossal whirlwinds of power, your blows are truly terrible. [Your Arete craves saturation, offering you someone else's life in exchange for longevity in red velvet.]

Your wisdom surpasses most mortals, and students have even begun to reach out to you. Ghor can no longer distort you.[Your Arete is able to speak like the wind, change the essence of things, dance, pretend to be human... A man dressed in white...]

Knowledge of all spheres has been achieved, titanic work has been done. You close your eyes and surrender to the power of calm thoughts [There is so much light inside you that now you hide it in the glare of rooms, the cracks of doors and shadows. Аrete sings in happines, maybe you will become weird to others.]

Nobody understands you anymore. Only Udrazen would understand, but he has been gone for a long time, you are moving away from people in search of unforgettableness.[Arete unlockes new edges od relity to you, your cognito splites between new ways.]
You ascended to the level of a mortal-god out of will, but perhaps you can become something more [Your Arete shines and shimmers in unimaginable forms . It's almost perfect].

Now you are one of the gods of this reality, you have achieved the impossible and become a god. A real god. You have reached the highest level without losing yourself. [Your Arete eclipses the sky and the stars. You are free from your shackles..
